```plantuml
@startuml blockchain-signaling-system_bloss-core

actor User as U
participant "Stalk" as S
participant "BloSS" as B
participant "Pollen" as P
participant "Ethereum Blockchain" as EB
participant "InfluxDB" as IDB
participant "IPFS" as IPFS

U -> S: Initiate Network Traffic Monitoring
activate S
S -> S: Analyze Traffic Patterns
S -> S: Detect Potential Attack
S -> B: Report Potential Attack
deactivate S

activate B
B -> B: Handle Mitigation Request
B -> P: Request Attack Report Storage
deactivate B

activate P
P -> EB: Record Attack Report
P -> IPFS: Store Encrypted Attack Report
P -> IDB: Record Traffic Statistics
deactivate P

P -> B: Confirm Attack Report Stored
activate B
B -> U: Respond to User with Status
deactivate B

@enduml
```